    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>This guide provides information on how to go about engaging and arranging payment for a casual worker to undertake a short term assignment for the University.</p>
<p>If you have any questions regarding this process please email <a href="mailto:casualstaff@qmu.ac.uk" title="QMU Casual Worker Email">casualpayments@qmu.ac.uk</a> <br /><br /><strong>Human Resources </strong><br /><strong>2023</strong></p>]]></Value>
